channel.title: StickRPG cheat client
channel.description:
I got bored so i decided to play around with shockwave flash in vb and my brother was using a adventure quest cheat client at the time so i wanted to start developing one.
So far it just has small features like money form where u enter how many coins you want also a skateboard,knife and a gun and ammo spawn withc spawn in your backpack and stat increase and hp increase.
